column5: Happy Birthday Glen!!  May your days be sunny and your tackle box stay dry, and may you catch a big one every time you try!!!  Best to you!! Carole
Happy birthday G! Seems a good reason the enjoy a beverage in your honour! -Brian
HAPPY B-DAY THERE SOUTHERN OLDE,TIMMER !!!!!!now why dont you really impress us and have another 60 or so of those..LOL..LOL.  . cheers buddy
Happy Birthday Buddy!!!!!!!  Hope you had a fantastic day and got what you wanted  Joey
Belated HAPPY BIRTHDAY !!  Glen. Hope you had a great day.  Feels good to be "Plenty Nine" EH !!!
....Oh boy I love B'days, especially when they ain't mine. Hope your day was swill Glen
How did I miss this Happy birthday Glen.  Regards, Sam
Best Fishes, and a Happy Birthday to my friend Glen.  'member your first Nipissing pike?  Hope to do that again shortly, good health to ya.  And Cheryl, too, the woman is a saint.
Many happy returns Glen
Belated Happy Birthday Glen....  Hope it was a good one...
It's after 6 and he's still in bed...I'd say it was a decent birfday.
Doogle was that the one he caught or the one he got to hold

Believe it or not, I actually caught that fish! douG did a darn good job puting me on that fish and I always remember that day! I was throwing and X Rap and had just finished telling douG how I'd never caught anything on an X Rap when that Pike hit... I guess he heard me and felt sorry for me.  Thanks again for all the wonderful Birthday wishes!!!  Y'all are the BEST!!!  Glen
Hey Dawg...I found your cake...!!!!!!!!!!!!!
That PBR makes a Mi-T-Fine shrimp boil Beans!!!

Happy Birthday my friend.Glad to have met you in November.  My life has changed since I met you skunkings now come in the third degree from you.  Glen always a pleasure to read your reports they make my day.especially during this thawless time now get out and shore fish will ya
A happy day to you my friend with health, happiness and even a few wall-ices in the coming season.
Hope you have a super birthday and get some fishing in.
Glen type dawg? Have a good one!
happy bday!  cheers!
Yeah Paul. The shirtless, Alabananas type Dawg.
Alabananas say that 3 times fast Roy.
Happy B-Day  young feller, and all the best to ya !!!!
Of course...the Ides of March...A Very Happy Birthday to you....Enjoy.
Thanks a bunch y'all!!!  I'd have rather been born on St. Patty's day, but you take what you can get when wimmins are involved.
Happy bday Glen, have a great day.
Have a good one Glen, all the best to you on this day, and may you have man more in health and happiness
Happy Birthday Glen. I hope you have a great day and many more.
The big 24 this year..eh?
24??  Oh, ok, you mean in Dawg years, eh?
Happy birthday! Eh you Hoser!  G
Hope you have a great B-day , Dawg...Many Happy returns and Sabiki rigged successes
Happy Birthday bud....have a good one
Happy birthday Dawg have a great day  Rob
Many Happy returns my friend...Dang Dawg...You're catching up to me pretty quick...  HEY...Where's the cake...I can't find the cake...  I likes CAKE !...
Happy Happy Birthday !!!!!  Gottca a lil something old buddy but you got to get it in June at Lakair   Cheers !!!
Happy Birthday my friend.    May there be a fish on each hook of your infamous sabiki rig.
That's where all that wind came from down 'Bama way... Glen blowing out his candles!  Have a good day Glen !
Happy Birthday ya ole fart!
Happy B-Day Dawg, tight lines and happy times!!  Stan
Hey Glen...hope you have a GREAT day!  Best wishes...hope you get all you want!!!  So, how old are ya anyways??? LOL
